{"tid":1959650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】黃山免費入場 2萬人蜂擁而至 景區緊急關閉","createTime":"2020-04-05T14:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T14:28:32.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0dbf3a3c7e47bb441cdfabbbdf870568b3ffce","tid":1959650,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情未過，一直待在家中的民眾已經按捺不住。不少安徽民眾趁着清明節假期、高速公路免收費、黃山景區免收安徽居民入場費，紛紛湧到黃山景區希望可以「出來走走」。可是，景區昨、今兩日一早擠滿遊客，高峯期更錄得2萬人次的入場上限，景區需要緊急關閉。<br />\n<br />\n今早約7時50分，黃山風景區管委會發出公告，指景區進山人數已達到遊客流量限制的2萬人次，已停止遊客入園，要求遊客選擇其他旅遊路線，或改日進山。其他熱門景區預計今天也會實施限流管控措施，呼籲今、明到黃山市的遊客要「合理安排出行時間，錯峯出遊」。<br />\n<br />\n據報，大批車輛塞在前往黃山的高速公路上，動彈不得，而進入黃山景區的民眾，入場前要先取得綠色健康碼，同時亦需先前預約時間進山。"},{"pid":"11e793910d20e928aa1847cda198e78df26e3730","tid":1959650,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"黃山附近的景區實施限制人流措施，當中西遞遊客限量在1.6萬人次，宏村景區遊客限量在1.8萬人次，呈坎和唐模景區各限制在1萬人次，棠樾牌坊群限制在7,500人次，徽州古城1萬人次，新安江山水畫廊為3,375人次。<br />\n<br />\n安徽網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200405/TAQGSEG5CHASEOP7E775LPNC64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200405%2FTAQGSEG5CHASEOP7E775LPNC64%2F&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=0db02463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200405%2FTAQGSEG5CHASEOP7E775LPNC64%2F&h=38eba5a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200405/TAQGSEG5CHASEOP7E775LPNC64/</a>"},{"pid":"7578014ccd74efa41d15e905cf28ff73c45920c5","tid":1959650,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5430115842f61d6da8bd1769be67f7c6d4a4a102","tid":1959650,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/b8z_ZlZJQRxMVYGDPAopLacwpZg=/346x194/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XNMLFHLA3A432NMZPMKLOJU5YQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fb8z_ZlZJQRxMVYGDPAopLacwpZg%3D%2F346x194%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXNMLFHLA3A432NMZPMKLOJU5YQ.jpg&h=436a788b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba9dce3380dc2b7563ab283c3783b6e7f8b731f9","tid":1959650,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/tyQYjolqcXSAPnQKeEi9YaoswAg=/346x194/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/IU7NKLCKECMG52VKMZQ6HI65YU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FtyQYjolqcXSAPnQKeEi9YaoswAg%3D%2F346x194%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FIU7NKLCKECMG52VKMZQ6HI65YU.jpg&h=5c6e7026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53da33b9a6ddf46b7724a2a39ede87c85835fd4d","tid":1959650,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200405/s00004/df7d88dbca995af2051e4672c153d10c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200405%2Fs00004%2Fdf7d88dbca995af2051e4672c153d10c.jpg&h=b3275fde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dad98f1ffa4a6d885f765103fddd6ea2a253d06","tid":1959650,"uid":103050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"有咩好驚？<br />\n支共一早打贏左武肺<br />\n仲要悼念日都搞埋<br />\n唔通再爆過兩個月後又悼念多次咩？"},{"pid":"daf2b103b1da49a85a35906edc3fcf680374afeb","tid":1959650,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢啲。咁先有無限次爆發"},{"pid":"617b86f463d524d3601386a340f52f4d171e01d2","tid":1959650,"uid":85